text: Pine Lake is a lake in Duxbury, Massachusetts in the village of Tinkertown. The lake is located southwest of Round Pond, northwest of Island Creek Pond, and east of Route 3 near the East Street underpass. The outflow is a small stream that flows into Round Pond. A small subdivision lies along the southern shore of the lake. ==References== ==External links== *Environmental Protection Agency *South Shore Coastal Watersheds - Lake Assessments Category:Lakes of Plymouth County, Massachusetts Category:Duxbury, Massachusetts Category:Reservoirs in Massachusetts
